{"tid":762063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla傳洽商歐洲建立「超級工廠」","createTime":"2018-07-31T03:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T07:00:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f72dcdf48f9db103d8509c27b099f00c620badc6","tid":762063,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"Tesla傳洽商歐洲建立「超級工廠」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1903428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1903428&d=ZwXxiz8aJHjnUpSvs3T%2F7hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=48f98350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1903428</a><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述歐洲官員稱，美國電動車生產商特斯拉(Tesla)正與德國及荷蘭政府洽商，在當地設立歐洲首間供應電池的「超級工廠」(Gigafactory)。<br />\n<br />\n根據報道，特斯拉與兩個德國州政府初步接觸，研究在當地興建超級電池工廠與電動車生產廠的可能性。不過，有關洽談屬於早期階段，未有任何協定。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉行政總裁馬斯克在6月時曾經在Twitter表示，如果一定要在歐洲興建超級工廠，德國是他心目中的首選地方，例如在德法邊境地區。特斯拉在德國已有一個工程基地，位置便是在上述德法邊境區。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉發言人拒評上述消息。本月較早時，該公司宣布在上海設立「超級工廠」。"},{"pid":"85ddce574a58f09803ccb4758101539b1caf8487","tid":762063,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7360a314a2de72b717d7cd9d4e966887fced071f","tid":762063,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T06:49:55.000Z","msg":"電池production 污染好大"},{"pid":"07b2c7dac271821efb9560c326ba43db91eef9f5","tid":762063,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好多大廠 會唔會俾人針死"}]}